news, industry analysis, and more.


4. HOW TO USE POWERIZE

Powerize makes it easy to search our more than 10,000 sources of
business and investment research to find just what you're looking for. 
Several of our more popular features include:

* Simple Search: the easiest way to search Powerize, right from our
homepage. Here's an example of Simple Search results, about Microsoft:

http://wwwrd.0mm.com/pwz536001

* Advanced Search: Powerize's Advanced Search page enables you to 
search for words in an article's headline, specify a date range for your 
search, and select categories of content for your search.

* Industry Updates: each Industry Update features important industry
news stories from around the world, culled from thousands of
Powerize's brand-name sources and constantly updated throughout
the day. All of the content on Industry Updates is available for free
to Powerize members. You'll find links to our Industry Updates
on the homepage. Here's an example of one of the Industry Updates:

http://wwwrd.0mm.com/pwz536002

Other popular features of Powerize include our free Powerize Alerts 
(see below), free Industry News Digests (see below), and our Editor's 
Choice daily email newsletter. You'll begin to receive our Editor's 
Choice newsletter soon. If you'd like to opt out of receiving the 
Editor's Choice newsletter, simply follow the "unsubscribe" instructions 
on the newsletter.


5. HOW TO SET UP YOUR FREE POWERIZE ALERTS

Powerize offers our members the best free alert service on the Internet.  
Powerize Alerts monitor our 10,000+ publications and other sources for 
new information about the subjects that are important to you, and 
automatically notify you by email whenever we receive new articles or 
reports about those subjects.  

Take a few minutes right now to set up your free Powerize Alerts right 
here. You'll need your Powerize User ID and Password to login to the 
alerts setup page:

http://wwwrd.0mm.com/pwz536003

6. HOW TO SUBSCRIBE TO FREE INDUSTRY NEWS DIGESTS

