8. FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS ABOUT POWERIZE.COM

Here are the answers to some of the questions we get asked most often
about Powerize. You'll find answers to other frequently asked
questions about Powerize at

http://www.powerize.com/pubdoc/faq.kml.


Q. Where can I find a list of the free information sources at Powerize?
A. You'll find downloadable catalogs of all of our titles, as well as
a link to a sample list of titles, at

http://www.corp.powerize.com/prodsserv/contentsources.htm


Q. Why isn't all of the information at Powerize free?
A. Powerize is the first site on the Internet to offer access to so
much premium full-text content for free. Much of this information has
never been available to business users for free before now. As our
business grows, we will be able to make more and more of the content in
our collection available for free. Several of our key content sources
will not be available for free anytime soon, though. Truly premium
content such as brokerage research reports will only be available on a
pay-per-view basis.

Q. How can I change my account information?
A. To change your password, review or modify your account information,
or cancel your membership, go to

http://www.powerize.com/pubdoc/youraccount.kml


Q. There are many people in my organization who would benefit by getting
free access to business research content at Powerize. How can I make
it available to them?
A. Start by completing and submitting our Enterprise Account Information
Request form. A member of our staff will contact you. You can access
the form at

http://www.corp.powerize.com/enterprise


